## Code Review Report — Past 24 Hours

### Files Reviewed (28 commits, 90+ files)
**Source code:** `quadratic-parser.ts`, `canvas-utils.ts`, `InterceptIdentification.tsx`, `HintPanel.tsx`, `PhaseRenderer.tsx`, `ConvexClientProvider.tsx`, `app/layout.tsx`, `audit.ts`
